About this item

  • PCI-Express X1 to NGFF M.2 2230 Interface (Key E/A+E) wireless wifi adapter with SMA Antenna
  • WiFi signal goes through PCIe X1 interface, and Bluetooth signal goes through USB interface (Bluetooth USB cable is included)
  • Bluetooth USB cable is used to connect the adapter to the motherboard USB port for Bluetooth function
  • Triple Band 2.4GHz 5GHz 6GHz Antenna: 6 dBi RP-SMA Male antenna, with 2 x 15cm U.FL/IPEX4 to RP-SMA Female pigtail cable
  • Only work with NGFF M.2 2230 Interface (Key E/A+E) wireless network card, such as Intel AX210NGW, AX200NGW, 9260NGW, 8265NGW, 8260NGW, 7265NGW, 7260NGW, and Broadcom, Realtek, Atheros NGFF M.2 2230 Interface (Key E/A+E) wireless network card. Support WiFi 4/5/6/6E, Bluetooth 4.0/4.1/4.2/5.0/5.1/5.2
  • To be noted: can not work with M.2 CNVio2/CNVio interface wireless network card, such as intel AX211NGW, AX201NGW, AC 9560NGW, AC 9462NGW, AC 9461NGW, etc.
  • To be noted: can not work with Mini PCIe wireless network card
  • Only regular-profile mounting bracket, no low-profile mounting bracket
  • To be noted: This item is only a signal converter, and does not has any driver. But you may need to install a driver for your M.2 NGFF Key E/A+E Wireless Network Card
  • OS compatibility: DOS/Windows/Linux/Mac OS (Base on your WiFi Card Compatibility)

Product Description

Model: WA01

Interface to PC PCI-Express x1
Interface to WiFi module E Key
WiFi Compatibility WiFi 4/5/6/6E/7
Bluetooth Compatibility Bluetooth 4.0/4.1/4.2/5.0/5.1/5.2/5.3/5.4
Antenna 6 dBi RP-SMA Male antenna, with 2 x 15cm U.FL/IPEX4 to RP-SMA Female pigtail cable
M.2 E-Key WiFi Module BE200NGW, AX210NGW, AX200NGW, 9260NGW, 8265NGW, 8260NGW, 7265NGW, 7260NGW, etc
Support Coral TPU (M.2 Accelerator A+E key)

PCIe X1 to NGFF M.2 Key E/A+E WiFi Adapter

SMA Antenna

  • 6 dBi RP-SMA Male Antenna
  • 2 x 15cm U.FL/IPEX4 to RP-SMA Female pigtail cable
  • Frequency range supported: 2.4GHz, 5GHz-6GHz Antenna

Bluetooth Cable

Bluetooth cable is used to connect the adapter to the motherboard USB port for Bluetooth function

Insulating Tape

As the IPEX4 interface is very small, it is easy to fall off when snapping the network card interface, so cover the IPEX4 interface with insulating tape so that it will not fall off.

Fit for

  • Support M.2 Key-E/A+E WiFi module, such as Intel AX210NGW, AX200NGW, 9260NGW, 8265NGW, 8260NGW, 7265NGW, 7260NGW, etc
  • Support Coral TPU - M.2 Accelerator A+E key
  • Note: Can not work with M.2 CNVio2/CNVio interface WiFi modular, such as intel AX211NGW, AX201NGW, AC 9560NGW, AC 9462NGW, AC 9461NGW, etc.

The package includes

  1. WA01
  2. 2 x 6 dBi RP-SMA Antenna
  3. Bluetooth Cable
  4. 8cm Low-profile Bracket
  5. Screw Driver
  6. 2 x Insulating Tape
  7. Screws for mounting to PC chassis
  8. Screws for WiFi module Installation

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Reviewed in France on 30 August 2024
